### Get a Product by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products/{{PRODUCT_ID}}

### List Products
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products?page=2&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc

### Search Products by Name
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products?name=laptop&page=1&size=10

### Search Products by Price Range
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products?minPrice=1000000&maxPrice=5000000&sort=cogm,asc

### Search Products by Stock Range
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products?minStock=20&maxStock=50&sort=stock,desc

### Filter Products by Stock
GET {{BASE_URL}}/products?available=true
### Chane to false for out of Stock Products

